<placeName cert="high">Philadelphia</placeName></head><div lang="grc" part="N" type="edition"><ab part="N">
    <lb n="1"/>Λονγεῖνος Ὁστιλλίῳ τῷ ἀδελφῷ 

    <lb n="2"/><expan>χ<ex cert="high">αίρειν</ex></expan>. πρὸ τῶν ὅλων εὔχομαι <choice><corr>ὑμᾶς</corr><sic>ημας</sic></choice> ὑγιαί-

    <lb n="3"/><choice><corr>νειν</corr><sic>υγιαινιν</sic></choice> μετὰ καὶ τῶν ἀβασκάντων μου 

    <lb n="4"/>παιδίων. θαυμάζω πῶς ὀρθο<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">π</unclear>ο<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">δ</unclear>ου-

    <lb n="5"/>τες καὶ <choice><corr>πέμψαντός</corr><sic>πεμψατος</sic></choice> μου καὶ ἐπιστό-

    <lb n="6"/>λιν διὰ Οὐαλεριανοῦ τοῦ Νεστοποι-

    <lb n="7"/>κίτου, ἀνθρώπου ἀσφαλοῦς, οὐ πισ-

    <lb n="8"/>τεύω ὅτι οὐ παρεκόμισε <choice><corr>ὑμῖν</corr><sic>ημιν</sic></choice> τὸ ἐ-

    <lb n="9"/>πιστόλιν ἐμοῦ <choice><corr>καταδιώξαντος</corr><sic><subst><add place="inline">κ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ατ</unclear>αδιοξαντος</add><del rend="corrected">κα<gap extent="1" reason="illegible" unit="character"/>αδιοξαντος</del></subst></sic></choice> ἄχρι 

    <lb n="10"/>τοῦ Ἑλικῶνος, καὶ διὰ τοῦ τῆς 

    <lb n="11"/>Μαρκίας ἔπεμψα <choice><corr>ὑμῖν</corr><sic>ημιν</sic></choice> τὴν λί-

    <lb n="12"/>τραν ἐπὶ τὴν πύλην αὐτὸν εὑρών, 

    <lb n="13"/><choice><corr>λέγει</corr><sic>λεγι</sic></choice> <choice><corr>εἰς</corr><sic>ις</sic></choice> τὴν πύλην <choice><corr>εἰς</corr><sic>ις</sic></choice> <choice><corr>Φιλαδελφείαν</corr><sic>φιλαδελφια<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ν</unclear></sic></choice> 

    <lb n="14"/><choice><corr>ἐπιτηρεῖν</corr><sic>επιτηριν</sic></choice> καὶ οὐδὲ ἐπιστόλιν 

    <lb n="15"/>μοι ἐπέμψατε οὐδὲ οὐδεμίαν 

    <lb n="16"/>φάσιν. καλῶς <choice><corr>ποιήσετε</corr><sic>ποιησιτε</sic></choice> πέμψα-

    <lb n="17"/><choice><corr>ντες</corr><sic>πενψατες</sic></choice> περὶ τῆς σωτηρίας <choice><corr>ὑμῶν</corr><sic>ημων</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="18"/>ἧς <choice><corr>μείζω</corr><sic>μιζω</sic></choice> οὐκ ἔχω, ἢ <choice><corr>ὑμῖν</corr><sic>ημιν</sic></choice> οὐ <choice><corr>μέλει</corr><sic>μελι</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="19"/>περὶ ἐμοῦ· ἐμοὶ δὲ <choice><corr>μέλει</corr><sic>μελι</sic></choice> περὶ ὑ-

    <lb n="20"/><choice><corr>μῶν</corr><sic>ημων</sic></choice> καίπερ <choice><corr>ὑμῶν</corr><sic>ημων</sic></choice> <choice><corr>εἰς</corr><sic>ις</sic></choice> τὰ περὶ πό-

    <lb n="21"/>λιν πύκνα <choice><corr>ἔξωθεν</corr><sic>εξ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ο</unclear>θεν</sic></choice> τῶν πυλῶν, 

    <lb n="22"/>τάχα <choice><corr>ὑμῖν</corr><sic>ημιν</sic></choice> ἐνπέσῃ τι κολπι-

    <lb n="23"/>τευόμενον μή πως <choice><corr>ἐπηρεία</corr><sic>επερια</sic></choice> μοι 

    <lb n="24"/>γένηται ἵνα <choice><corr>γινώσκητε</corr><sic>γεινωσκητε</sic></choice> ποῦ 

    <lb n="25"/>εἰμι καὶ <choice><corr>εἰς</corr><sic>ις</sic></choice> <choice><corr>ποῖον</corr><sic>ποιν</sic></choice> τόπον εἶμι, ἀλ-

    <lb n="26"/>λὰ ἅπαξ οὐ <choice><corr>μέλει</corr><sic>με<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">λι</unclear></sic></choice> <choice><corr>ὑμῖν</corr><sic>ημιν</sic></choice> περὶ ἐμοῦ. 

    <lb n="27"/>καλῶς οὖν ποιήσετε σπεύσαντες 

    <lb n="28"/>τοῦ <choice><corr>ἀνελθεῖν</corr><sic>α<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ν</supplied>ελθιν</sic></choice> πρὸς ἐμὲ ἀπαρτίσαν-


    <lb n="29"/>τες <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">τα</supplied>χ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ύ</unclear>. θέλω δὲ διά τινος πισ-

    <lb n="30"/>τοῦ <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">π</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">έ</supplied>μψαι <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ὑ</supplied>μῖν τὸν χαλκὸν ὡς 

    <lb n="31"/>προέγραψα <choice><corr>ὑμῖν</corr><sic>ημ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ιν</supplied></sic></choice>. <choice><corr>ἐρρῶσθαι</corr><sic>ερρωσσθαι</sic></choice> <choice><corr>ὑμᾶς</corr><sic>ημας</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="32"/>ἐπὶ <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">π</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ο</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">λλ</unclear>ῶν· ἀσ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">πά</unclear>ζ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ο</unclear>μαι κατ᾽ ὄνομα 

    <lb n="33"/>πάν<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">τ</supplied>ας καὶ πά<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">σ</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ας</unclear>, πατέρα μου, Διόδω-

    <lb n="34"/>ραν <gap extent="2" reason="lost" unit="character"/>ικαριο<gap extent="2" reason="illegible" unit="character"/><gap extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="character"/> 


    <lb n="29"/>τες <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">τα</supplied>χ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ύ</unclear>. θέλω δὲ διά τινος πισ-

    <lb n="30"/>τοῦ <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">π</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">έ</supplied>μψαι <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ὑ</supplied>μῖν τὸν χαλκὸν ὡς 

    <lb n="31"/>προέγραψα <choice><corr>ὑμῖν</corr><sic>ημ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ιν</supplied></sic></choice>. <choice><corr>ἐρρῶσθαι</corr><sic>ερρωσσθαι</sic></choice> <choice><corr>ὑμᾶς</corr><sic>ημας</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="32"/>ἐπὶ <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">π</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ο</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">λλ</unclear>ῶν· ἀσ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">πά</unclear>ζ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ο</unclear>μαι κατ᾽ ὄνομα 

    <lb n="33"/>πάν<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">τ</supplied>ας καὶ πά<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">σ</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ας</unclear>, πατέρα μου, Διόδω-

    <lb n="34"/>ραν <gap extent="2" reason="lost" unit="character"/>ικαριο<gap extent="2" reason="illegible" unit="character"/><gap extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="character"/> </ab></div><div n="meta.27218" part="N" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.27218" part="N" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date notAfter="200" notBefore="176" type="textDate">Ende II</date></p></div><div n="meta.27218" part="N" subtype="general" type="commentary"><p>Zu Z. 32-33 vgl. Festschrift E. Berti, S. 26, Anm. 14.</p></div><div n="meta.27218" part="N" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl><bibl subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Phil.</title><biblScope type="numbers">35</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">27218</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP"><series>0188</series>; ; <biblScope type="numbers">35</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0188;;35" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.27218" part="N" subtype="illustrations" type="bibliography"><p><bibl type="illustration">Pl. VIII</bibl></p></div><div n="meta.27218" part="N" subtype="locations" type="history"><p>unbekannt</p></div><div n="meta.27218" part="N" type="figure"><p><figure href="http://ipap.csad.ox.ac.uk/4DLink4/4DACTION/IPAPwebquery?vPub=P.Phil.&amp;vVol=&amp;vNum=35"><figDesc>Abbildung im Internet</figDesc></figure></p></div></body></text></TEI.2>